casebody.data:
Gaylord et al., Respondents, v. Rinaldo, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 14, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Larremore, O. J., and Bookstaver, J.

Hays & Greenbaum, for appellant. John E. Eustis, for respondents.

No opinion. Ordered that the judgment be affirmed, with costs.
